\textbf{Prove or Disprove}

\textbf{For this problem, \emph{clearly indicate} whether the statement
is \emph{true or false} then prove or disprove it.}

If $\displaystyle \phi(n)|n - 1$ then \emph{n} is squarefree. (Here
$\displaystyle \phi$ is the Euler $\displaystyle \phi$-function.)
